
Agar isi data ko UPDATE karna ho, to syntax kuch is tarah hoga:

UPDATE employees
SET salary = 80000,
    designation = 'Senior Backend Developer'
WHERE email = 'rahul.sharma@gmail.com';


Agar Rahul ka department aur salary update karna ho:

UPDATE employees
SET department = 'Software Development',
    salary = 90000
WHERE emp_id = 1;


Agar sabhi IT employees ki salary ₹5000 badhani ho:

UPDATE employees
SET salary = salary + 5000
WHERE emp_id = 1;




